## Enforcement Timeline

### Phase 1: Awareness & Education (Feb-Aug 2025)
- Regulatory guidance published
- Industry outreach campaigns
- Voluntary compliance programs

### Phase 2: Proactive Enforcement (Aug 2025 - Feb 2026)
- Monitoring and inspections begin
- Warning letters issued
- Corrective actions required

### Phase 3: Full Enforcement (Feb 2026+)
- Full inspection regime
- Fines for non-compliance
- Product recalls for prohibited systems

## Business Impact Timeline

### Short-Term (0-6 months)
- Immediate cessation of prohibited AI
- Initial AI inventory
- Governance structure setup

### Medium-Term (6-18 months)
- Compliance implementation
- Documentation creation
- Staff training
- Conformity assessments

### Long-Term (18+ months)
- Ongoing monitoring
- Post-market surveillance
- Continuous improvement
- Regulatory updates

